window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>With second chances come new challenges....</p> <p>Peter Busch-McGinley is living his best life in Fertile Valley. He's making up for lost time with his daughter, bringing his grandpa's farm back to its former glory, and keeping up with his new duties as the Harvest Goddess' champion.</p> <p>Yet a new darkness lurks in the woods. Mysterious shadows that feed on people's emotions, all working for an ominous creature that lives deep beneath the mine. He'll have to rely on help from an unlikely source to set things back on track again.</p> <p>Can Pete find a way to work with the Queen of the Mines to save Fertile Valley? Or will the darkness claim them both?</p>"; 
